rows.label: qst201405_msg0025
rows.name: Hmmm... It's kind of quiet.

rows.label: qst201405_msg0026
rows.name:
Looks like everyone's just hanging
back in their rooms.

rows.label: qst201405_msg0001
rows.name:
Well, we may as well pass the time...
Hikari. Why don't you ask me what
my favorite food is?

rows.label: qst201405_msg0027
rows.name:
Okay! Well... Zakuro, what is your
favorite food?

rows.label: qst201405_msg0002
rows.name:
My favorite food is...wait for it...
Fleur Bavarian!

rows.label: qst201405_msg0003
rows.name:
I like the little white flowers inside.
And it has this appealing wobbly
texture to it.

rows.label: qst201405_msg0004
rows.name:
It's smooth and sweet when it hits
your tongue...

rows.label: qst201405_msg0005
rows.name:
Yeah...I don't think it'd be hyperbole
to say that foods like Fleur Bavarian
boost one's Girl Power by 1,000%.

rows.label: qst201405_msg0006
rows.name:
Hey, come on. You're exaggerating,
again.

rows.label: qst201405_msg0007
rows.name:
Huh?
Well, how about you, Hikari?

rows.label: qst201405_msg0008
rows.name:
For me, it's gotta be Cloud Sea Crab
Sticks!

rows.label: qst201405_msg0009
rows.name: Seriously?

rows.label: qst201405_msg0010
rows.name:
Yeah! Crunchy on the outside, soft on
the inside!

rows.label: qst201405_msg0011
rows.name:
If you ask me, it's the best way to get
the full flavor of Cloud Sea crab!

rows.label: qst201405_msg0012
rows.name:
No no no, come on... You can't seriously...
Crab sticks? Really? They're just a bit...

rows.label: qst201405_msg0013
rows.name:
Well, to be honest, they're the kind of
thing that brings your Girl Power down
instead of boosting it.

rows.label: qst201405_msg0014
rows.name:
Hey! What's wrong with Cloud Sea
Crab Sticks? They're lovely!

rows.label: qst201405_msg0015
rows.name:
Zakuro. Don't you think going crazy over
sweet things is a bit, well...basic?

rows.label: qst201405_msg0016
rows.name:
Well, I.M.H.O., they're a lot better than
fishy old crab sticks!

rows.label: qst201405_msg0017
rows.name:
I think we can both agree I won this
round. I've got the most Girl Power.

rows.label: qst201405_msg0018
rows.name: I think not!

rows.label: qst201405_msg0019
rows.name:
I hardly think we can declare a winner
without a judge!

rows.label: qst201405_msg0020
rows.name:
And this wasn't really a proper test...
It was just a bit of chit-chat. You can't
just make up rules like that!

rows.label: qst201405_msg0021
rows.name: Yeah, I guess you're right.

rows.label: qst201405_msg0022
rows.name:
Hmmm... Doesn't look like anyone's
going to show up though...

rows.label: qst201405_msg0024
rows.name: But we need to settle this!
